snippet.title: Inn Tycoon | Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
*Correction: Game released on Aug 26, 2024!*

Inn Tycoon is a relaxing and enjoyable game, offering you the opportunity to build, design, and manage your own inn! We're thrilled to announce that our cozy inn management game, is coming to Steam Early Access on Aug 28, 2024!

Buy Now: https://s.team/a/2749000

Please follow us:
